useImportType.option:
This rule respects thejsxRuntimesetting and will make an exception for React globals if it is set to"reactClassic".
styleSection titled “style”
Thestyleoption allows enforcing a style for importing types.
The option supports three values:
inlineType: always use import { type T } instead of import type { T }
separatedType: always use import type { T } instead of import { type T }
auto: use both import type { T } and import { type T } (default)
